sourcesContent: import React from 'react' const UserPhone = ({user}) => { var gender = user.income var price = user.phone_price return ( <> { (gender === "Male") && (price > 10000) ? <> {user.id} {user.first_name} {user.last_name} {user.email} {user.gender} {user.income} {user.city} {user.car} {user.quote} {user.phone_price} : <> } ) } export default UserPhone
